---
title: One-Pan Toscana Couscous Skillet with Chicken Sausage & Kale
description: Sometimes, the best meals come together with your favorite fridge and pantry items all in one pan. Enter: this skillet dinner. This recipe has a delicious mix of creamy pearl couscous, Tuscan-spiced kale, and chicken sausage. And it’s all topped with gooey melted Italian cheese. Plus, it comes together in just 20 minutes. Are you ready to dig in?
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/one-pan-tuscana-couscous-skillet-de2f9c50.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/one-pan-tuscana-couscous-skillet-615c8da2f2126b73a841c3e4-000221ba.pdf
